2025-12-25 18:36:15.080 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (26ms) [Parameters=[@__postId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[PostId], [t].[Author], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Content], [t].[CreateAt], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[MetaDescription], [t].[MetaTitle], [t].[Slug], [t].[Title], [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [c0].[CommentId], [c0].[Author], [c0].[Content], [c0].[CreatedAt], [c0].[PostId], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[PostId], [p].[Author], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Content], [p].[CreateAt], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[MetaDescription], [p].[MetaTitle], [p].[Slug], [p].[Title], [c].[Id], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Posts] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[PostId] = @__postId_0
) AS [t]
